<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8B2C7F 0%, #4A1942 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
    }
    .content {
      background: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
    }
    .status-badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 10px 0;
    }
    .status-under_review { background: #fbbf24; color: #78350f; }
    .status-interview { background: #60a5fa; color: #1e3a8a; }
    .status-accepted { background: #34d399; color: #065f46; }
    .status-rejected { background: #f87171; color: #7f1d1d; }
    .info-box {
      background: white;
      padding: 20px;
      border-left: 4px solid #8B2C7F;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #E91E8C 0%, #8B2C7F 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 15px 30px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 25px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Application Status Update</h1>
    <p>Yae Publishing House</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear <%= @application.first_name %>,</p>
    
    <p>We have an update regarding your application for the <strong><%= @job.title %></strong> position at Yae Publishing House.</p>
    
    <div class="info-box">
      <p><strong>Application Status:</strong></p>
      <span class="status-badge status-<%= @new_status %>">
        <%= @new_status.titleize %>
      </span>
    </div>
    
    <% case @new_status %>
    <% when 'under_review' %>
      <p>Great news! Your application is now under review by our hiring team. We're carefully evaluating your qualifications and experience for this role.</p>
      <p>We'll be in touch soon with next steps.</p>
      
    <% when 'interview' %>
      <p>Congratulations! We'd like to invite you for an interview. Our recruitment team will be reaching out to you shortly to schedule a time that works for you.</p>
      <p>Please keep an eye on your email and phone for our call.</p>
      
    <% when 'accepted' %>
      <p>Congratulations! We're thrilled to offer you the position of <strong><%= @job.title %></strong> at Yae Publishing House!</p>
      <p>Our HR team will be in touch with you shortly with details about your offer, next steps, and onboarding process.</p>
      <p>Welcome to the Yae Publishing Gang</p>
      
    <% when 'rejected' %>
      <p>Thank you for your interest in the <strong><%= @job.title %></strong> position and for taking the time to apply to Yae Publishing House.</p>
      <p>After careful consideration, we've decided to move forward with other candidates whose qualifications more closely match our current needs.</p>
      <p>We encourage you to apply for other positions at Yae Publishing House that align with your skills and experience. We'll keep your application on file for future opportunities.</p>
      
      <center>
        <a href="<%= careers_url %>" class="button">View Open Positions</a>
      </center>
    <% end %>
    
    <p>If you have any questions, please don't hesitate to reach out to us at <a href="mailto:<%= @job.contact_email || 'careers@yaepublishing.co.in' %>"><%= @job.contact_email || 'careers@yaepublishing.co.in' %></a>.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>
    <strong>The Yae Publishing House Career Services</strong></p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>